       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID.    COI58106.
      ******************************************************************
      *     PROGRAMA COI58106.                                         *
      *                                                                *
      *     Invoices                                                   *
      ******************************************************************
      *     LOG ALTERACOES:                                            *
      *   USER     / DATA     /   REFERENCIA / OBSERVACOES             *
      *                                                                *
      *                                                                *
      ******************************************************************
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       CONFIGURATION SECTION.
       DATA DIVISION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  FILLER                          PIC X(40) VALUE
           'INICIO WORKING-STORAGE COI58106         '.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            DECLARACOES DE DB2
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE COCD5013 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE COCD3605 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE COCD6405 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE COCD6900 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE SQLCA    END-EXEC.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            MENSAGEM DE INPUT E  OUTPUT
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY COCV5810.
       COPY COCV5811.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            AREAS DE TRABALHO
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY VIAL0010.
       COPY VIAL0015.
       COPY VIAW0005.
       COPY VIAK0001.
       COPY VIAK0002.
       COPY COCK0001.
       COPY COCK0002.
       COPY ETCK0001.
       COPY ETCK0002.
       COPY COCL5005.
       COPY ETCL0002.
       COPY AQCW0005.
       COPY COCL0030.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            CONSTANTES
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-CONSTANTES.
           05 CON-COVT3605 PIC X(08) VALUE 'COVT3605'.
           05 CON-COVT5013 PIC X(08) VALUE 'COVT5013'.
           05 CON-COVT6405 PIC X(08) VALUE 'COVT6405'.
           05 CON-COVT6900 PIC X(08) VALUE 'COVT6900'.
           05 CON-S        PIC X(01) VALUE 'S'.
           05 CON-N        PIC X(01) VALUE 'N'.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            VARIAVEIS
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-VARIAVEIS.
           05 WS-X                    PIC 9(03).
           05 WS-SEQ                  PIC S9(10)      COMP-3.
           05 WS-NIDINVOICE           PIC S9(10)      COMP-3.
           05 WS-NIDPROJECTO          PIC X(08).
           05 WS-GREFINV              PIC X(10).
           05 WS-IRECON               PIC X(01).
           05 WS-CPAIS                PIC X(03).
           05 WS-CBANCO               PIC X(04).
           05 WS-CCONTA               PIC X(34).
           05 WS-DDATMOV              PIC X(10).
           05 WS-NSEQMOV              PIC S9(05)      COMP-3.
           05 WS-CHAVE-NIDPROJECTO    PIC X(08).
           05 WS-CHAVE-NIDINVOICE     PIC S9(10)      COMP-3.
           05 WS-REG-64 OCCURS 100 TIMES.
            10 WS-REG-64-NIDINVOICE   PIC S9(10)      COMP-3.
            10 WS-REG-64-NSEQ         PIC S9(10)      COMP-3.
            10 WS-REG-64-NIDPROJECTO  PIC X(08).
            10 WS-REG-64-GCLIENTE     PIC X(255).
            10 WS-REG-64-DDATAINSER   PIC X(10).
            10 WS-REG-64-DDATAEMISS   PIC X(10).
            10 WS-REG-64-DDATAEMIS2   PIC X(10).
            10 WS-REG-64-DDATEDUE     PIC X(10).
            10 WS-REG-64-CPRAZO       PIC X(03).
            10 WS-REG-64-NTOTALAMOUNT PIC S9(15)V9(2) COMP-3.
            10 WS-REG-64-NTAXAMOUNT   PIC S9(15)V9(2) COMP-3.
            10 WS-REG-64-GDESCINVOICE PIC X(255).
            10 WS-REG-64-CSTATUS      PIC X(02).
            10 WS-REG-64-CUSERID      PIC X(20).
            10 WS-REG-64-HTIMEST      PIC X(26).
            10 WS-REG-64-GREFINV      PIC X(10).
            10 WS-REG-64-DPAG         PIC X(10).
            10 WS-REG-64-CTIPDOC      PIC X(02).
            10 WS-REG-64-CMOEDA       PIC X(03).
            10 WS-REG-64-CIMPOSTO     PIC X(05).
            10 WS-REG-64-NOTAS        PIC X(255).
            10 WS-REG-64-NTOTCTRV     PIC S9(15)V9(2) COMP-3.
            10 WS-REG-64-NTAXCTRV     PIC S9(15)V9(2) COMP-3.
            10 WS-REG-64-CTIPFAC      PIC X(2).
            10 WS-REG-64-NTOTPAG      PIC S9(15)V9(2) COMP-3.
            10 WS-REG-64-NTAXPAG      PIC S9(15)V9(2) COMP-3.
            10 WS-REG-64-NTOTRET      PIC S9(15)V9(2) COMP-3.
            10 WS-REG-64-NTAXRET      PIC S9(15)V9(2) COMP-3.
          05 WS-GAT-AMOUNT              PIC X(50)  VALUE SPACES.
          05 FILLER REDEFINES WS-GAT-AMOUNT.
             10 WS-GAT-NIDINVOICE       PIC S9(10).
             10 WS-GAT-AMOUNT-ANT       PIC S9(15)V9(2).
             10 WS-GAT-AMOUNT-POS       PIC S9(15)V9(2).
      ******************************************************************
      *  SWITCH
      ******************************************************************
       01  SW-SWITCHES.
           05 SW-RECONCILIACAO        PIC X(01) VALUE 'N'.
              88 SW-DESFAZ-RECONC               VALUE 'S'.
              88 SW-NAO-DESFAZ-RECONC           VALUE 'N'.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            PROGRAM CONTROL
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-PROGRAM-CONTROL.
           05 WS-PROGNAME     PIC  X(08) VALUE 'COI58106'.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *              DECLARACOES DE CURSORES DB2                     *
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-CURSOR-VARS.
           05 FILLER                     PIC X(01) VALUE SPACES.

           EXEC SQL
                DECLARE CURCOT64 CURSOR FOR
                 SELECT
                       NIDINVOICE
                     , NSEQ
                     , NIDPROJECTO
                     , GCLIENTE
                     , DDATAINSER
                     , DDATAEMISS
                     , DDATAEMIS2
                     , DDATEDUE
                     , CPRAZO
                     , NTOTALAMOUNT
                     , NTAXAMOUNT
                     , GDESCINVOICE
                     , CSTATUS
                     , CUSERID
                     , HTIMEST
                     , GREFINV
                     , DPAG
                     , CTIPDOC
                     , CMOEDA
                     , CIMPOSTO
                     , NOTAS
                     , NTOTCTRV
                     , NTAXCTRV
                     , CTIPFAC
                     , NTOTPAG
                     , NTAXPAG
                     , NTOTRET
                     , NTAXRET
                 FROM COVT6405_INVPAY
                 WHERE  NIDINVOICE  = :WS-NIDINVOICE
                    AND NIDPROJECTO = :WS-NIDPROJECTO

                  ORDER  BY NIDPROJECTO
                          , NIDINVOICE
           END-EXEC.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  FILLER                        PIC X(40) VALUE
           'FIM DA WORKING-STORAGE COI58106         '.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       LINKAGE SECTION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY VIAL0004.

            EXEC SQL INCLUDE VIAP0009 END-EXEC.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            0000-MAINLINE
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       0000-MAINLINE.

           PERFORM 1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
              THRU 1099-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

           PERFORM 2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
              THRU 2099-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

           PERFORM 3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA
              THRU 3099-FINAL-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

       0099-MAINLINE-EXIT.
           COPY VIAP0004.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-INPUT    TO COCV5810-MSG.
           MOVE COCV5810-ASE               TO COCV5811-ASE.

           INITIALIZE COCL5005-COMMAREA  REPLACING NUMERIC BY ZEROES
                                              ALPHANUMERIC BY SPACES.

           MOVE ZEROS                      TO COCL5005-NTOTALAMOUNT
           MOVE SPACES                     TO COCL5005-CIMPOSTO
           MOVE ZEROS                      TO COCL5005-NTAXAMOUNT
           MOVE ZEROS                      TO COCL5005-NRETAMOUNT
           MOVE ZEROS                      TO COCL5005-NRETTAX
           MOVE COCK0002-DATA-MIN          TO COCL5005-DDATAEMISS.

       1099-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2000-PROC-PROGRAMA.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2000-PROC-PROGRAMA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCV5810-ADE               TO COCV5811-ADE.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2100-VALIDACOES
                 THRU 2199-VALIDACOES-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF COCV5810-CIMPOSTO NOT = SPACES AND
                COCV5810-NTOTALAMOUNT NOT = ZEROS
                PERFORM 2100-VALIDA-IMPOSTO
                   THRU 2100-VALIDA-IMPOSTO-EXIT
             END-IF
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2200-MODIFICA-DADOS
                 THRU 2299-MODIFICA-DADOS-EXIT
           END-IF.

      *--- Actualiza campo Referencia na Tabela de Pagamentos
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2800-REFERENCIA
                 THRU 2800-REFERENCIA-EXIT
           END-IF.

       2099-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2100-VALIDACOES
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2100-VALIDACOES.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2100-VALIDACOES' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             PERFORM 2110-OBT-STATUS-ANT
                THRU 2110-OBT-STATUS-ANT-EXIT
           END-IF.

      *-----------------------------------------------------------*
      *--- Se o status da Factura for 3 (COCK0002-CSTATUS-PAG) ---*
      *--- e o status no ecran for 3 (COCK0002-CSTATUS-PAG)    ---*
      *--- dá erro pois năo aceita modificaçőes                ---*
      *-----------------------------------------------------------*
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF  COCD5013-CSTATUS EQUAL COCK0002-CSTATUS-PAG
             AND COCV5810-CSTATUS EQUAL COCK0002-CSTATUS-PAG
               MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
               MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV5811-CSTATUS-S
               MOVE COCK0001-STATUS-NMOD   TO COCV5811-CSTATUS-MSG
               MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC        TO COCV5811-CSTATUS-CAPLIC
             END-IF
           END-IF.

      *-----------------------------------------------------------*
      *--- Se foi emitida nota de credito, năo pode alterar    ---*
      *--- nenhum dos dados da factura                         ---*
      *-----------------------------------------------------------*
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF  COCD5013-NTOTNCR NOT EQUAL ZEROES OR
                 COCD5013-GREFNCR NOT EQUAL SPACES
               MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
               MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV5811-CSTATUS-S
               MOVE COCK0001-TEM-NOTA-CRED TO COCV5811-CSTATUS-MSG
               MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC        TO COCV5811-CSTATUS-CAPLIC
             END-IF
           END-IF.

      *-----------------------------------------------------------*
      *--- Se já tiver recebimentos năo deixa alterar o valor  ---*
      *--- liquido nem o tipo de imposto                       ---*
      *-----------------------------------------------------------*
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF  ( COCD5013-NTOTPAG NOT EQUAL ZEROS
             OR    COCD5013-NTAXPAG NOT EQUAL ZEROS )
             AND COCD5013-NTOTALAMOUNT NOT = COCV5810-NTOTALAMOUNT
               MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
               MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV5811-NTOTALAMOUNT-S
               MOVE COCK0001-VALOR-SEMALT  TO COCV5811-NTOTALAMOUNT-MSG
               MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC  TO COCV5811-NTOTALAMOUNT-CAPLIC
               MOVE COCD5013-NTOTALAMOUNT  TO COCV5811-NTOTALAMOUNT
             END-IF
           END-IF.
      *
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF COCD5013-NTOTALAMOUNT NOT = COCV5810-NTOTALAMOUNT
               PERFORM 2250-GERA-GATILHO
                  THRU 2250-GERA-GATILHO-EXIT
             END-IF
           END-IF.
      *
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF  ( COCD5013-NTOTPAG NOT EQUAL ZEROS
             OR    COCD5013-NTAXPAG NOT EQUAL ZEROS )
             AND COCD5013-CIMPOSTO NOT = COCV5810-CIMPOSTO
               MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
               MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV5811-CIMPOSTO-S
               MOVE COCK0001-IMPOS-SEMALT  TO COCV5811-CIMPOSTO-MSG
               MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC  TO COCV5811-CIMPOSTO-CAPLIC
               MOVE COCD5013-CIMPOSTO      TO COCV5811-CIMPOSTO
             END-IF
           END-IF.
      *
      *-----------------------------------------------------------*
      *
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF COCV5810-NTOTALAMOUNT  < ZEROS
               MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
               MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV5811-NTOTALAMOUNT-S
               MOVE COCK0001-SINAL-ERRADO  TO COCV5811-NTOTALAMOUNT-MSG
               MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC TO COCV5811-NTOTALAMOUNT-CAPLIC
             END-IF
           END-IF.
      *
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             EVALUATE TRUE
               WHEN COCV5810-REFINVOICE = SPACES
                    CONTINUE
               WHEN COCV5810-NTOTALAMOUNT < 0
                IF COCV5810-REFINVOICE(1:3) NOT NUMERIC  OR
                   COCV5810-REFINVOICE(4:1) NOT = '/'    OR
                   COCV5810-REFINVOICE(5:4) NOT NUMERIC  OR
                   COCV5810-REFINVOICE(9:2) NOT = SPACES
                   MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                   MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV5811-REFINVOICE-S
                   MOVE COCK0001-MASK-REF-INV TO COCV5811-REFINVOICE-MSG
                   MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC TO COCV5811-REFINVOICE-CAPLIC
                END-IF

               WHEN OTHER
                IF COCV5810-REFINVOICE(1:4) NOT NUMERIC  OR
                   COCV5810-REFINVOICE(5:1) NOT = '/'    OR
                   COCV5810-REFINVOICE(6:3) NOT NUMERIC  OR
                   COCV5810-REFINVOICE(9:2) NOT = SPACES
                   MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                   MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV5811-REFINVOICE-S
                   MOVE COCK0001-MASK-REF-INV TO COCV5811-REFINVOICE-MSG
                   MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC TO COCV5811-REFINVOICE-CAPLIC
                END-IF
             END-EVALUATE
           END-IF.

      *--- Năo pode alterar o estado da Factura para 4 - Anulada, para
      *--- isso deverá usar a transaçăo de Anulaçăo de Facturas
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
            IF COCV5810-CSTATUS EQUAL COCK0002-CSTATUS-ANUL
               MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
               MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV5811-CSTATUS-S
               MOVE COCK0001-ANUL-INV      TO COCV5811-CSTATUS-MSG
               MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC        TO COCV5811-CSTATUS-CAPLIC
            END-IF
           END-IF.
      *
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
      **R SE O E PAGO, VERIFICA SE O STATUS ANTERIOR JA ERA PAGO
      **R E SE NAO FOR, DA ERRO
      **R NESTA TRANSACAO NAO SE PERMITE PAGAR FACTURAS
             IF COCV5810-CSTATUS EQUAL COCK0002-CSTATUS-PAG
               IF COCV5810-DDATEPAG EQUAL COCK0002-DATA-MIN OR
                  COCV5810-DDATEPAG EQUAL SPACES
                 MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                 MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV5811-CSTATUS-S
                 MOVE COCK0001-DPAG-OBRIGAT TO COCV5811-CSTATUS-MSG
                 MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC TO COCV5811-CSTATUS-CAPLIC
               END-IF
               IF COCD5013-CSTATUS EQUAL COCK0002-CSTATUS-PAG
                 CONTINUE
               ELSE
                 MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                 MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV5811-CSTATUS-S
                 MOVE COCK0001-PAG-INV      TO COCV5811-CSTATUS-MSG
                 MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC TO COCV5811-CSTATUS-CAPLIC
               END-IF
             END-IF
           END-IF.

      **R QUANDO SE ANULA O PAGAMENTO, INICIALIZA OS SALDOS DE
      **R PAGAMENTO
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF COCD5013-CSTATUS EQUAL COCK0002-CSTATUS-PAG
               IF COCV5810-CSTATUS NOT EQUAL COCK0002-CSTATUS-PAG
                   MOVE ZEROES           TO COCD5013-NTOTPAG
                   MOVE ZEROES           TO COCD5013-NTAXPAG
                   MOVE COCD5013-NTOTPAG TO COCV5811-NVALREC
                   MOVE COCD5013-NTAXPAG TO COCV5811-NTAXREC
                   SET  SW-DESFAZ-RECONC TO TRUE
               END-IF
             END-IF
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF COCV5810-DDATEPAG NOT EQUAL COCK0002-DATA-MIN AND
                COCV5810-DDATEPAG NOT EQUAL SPACES
               IF COCV5810-CSTATUS < COCK0002-CSTATUS-PAG
                 MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                 MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV5811-CSTATUS-S
                 MOVE COCK0001-DDATPAG-INV  TO COCV5811-CSTATUS-MSG
                 MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC TO COCV5811-CSTATUS-CAPLIC
               END-IF
             END-IF
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF  COCV5810-DDATAEMIS2 NOT EQUAL COCK0002-DATA-MIN
               IF COCV5810-DDATEDUE LESS COCV5810-DDATAEMIS2
                 MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                 MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV5811-DDATEDUE-S
                 MOVE COCK0001-DVENC-MENOR   TO COCV5811-DDATEDUE-MSG
                 MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC        TO COCV5811-DDATEDUE-CAPLIC
               END-IF
             END-IF
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF  COCV5810-DDATAEMISS NOT EQUAL COCK0002-DATA-MIN
             AND COCV5810-DDATAEMIS2     EQUAL COCK0002-DATA-MIN
               IF COCV5810-DDATEDUE LESS COCV5810-DDATAEMISS
                 MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                 MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV5811-DDATEDUE-S
                 MOVE COCK0001-DVENC-MENOR   TO COCV5811-DDATEDUE-MSG
                 MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC        TO COCV5811-DDATEDUE-CAPLIC
               END-IF
             END-IF
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF COCV5810-DDATAEMIS2 NOT EQUAL COCK0002-DATA-MIN
               IF COCV5810-CSTATUS EQUAL COCK0002-CSTATUS-PEMISS OR
                  COCV5810-CSTATUS EQUAL COCK0002-CSTATUS-CANC   OR
                  COCV5810-CSTATUS EQUAL SPACES
                 MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                 MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV5811-CSTATUS-S
                 MOVE COCK0001-DEMIS-STATUS-INV TO COCV5811-CSTATUS-MSG
                 MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC TO COCV5811-CSTATUS-CAPLIC
               END-IF
             ELSE
               IF COCV5810-CSTATUS EQUAL COCK0002-CSTATUS-EMIT   OR
                  COCV5810-CSTATUS EQUAL COCK0002-CSTATUS-PPAG   OR
                  COCV5810-CSTATUS EQUAL COCK0002-CSTATUS-PAG    OR
                  COCV5810-CSTATUS EQUAL COCK0002-CSTATUS-ANUL
                 MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                 MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV5811-CSTATUS-S
                 MOVE COCK0001-DEMIS-STATUS-INV TO COCV5811-CSTATUS-MSG
                 MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC TO COCV5811-CSTATUS-CAPLIC
               END-IF
             END-IF
           END-IF.
      *
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF COCV5810-CPRAZO          EQUAL SPACES
                MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV5811-CPRAZO-S
                MOVE COCK0001-CAMPO-OBRIGAT TO COCV5811-CPRAZO-MSG
                MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC        TO COCV5811-CPRAZO-CAPLIC
             END-IF
           END-IF.
      *
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF COCV5810-CIMPOSTO        EQUAL SPACES
                MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV5811-CIMPOSTO-S
                MOVE COCK0001-CAMPO-OBRIGAT TO COCV5811-CIMPOSTO-MSG
                MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC        TO COCV5811-CIMPOSTO-CAPLIC
             END-IF
           END-IF.
      *
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF COCV5810-DDATAEMISS EQUAL SPACES OR
                COCV5810-DDATAEMISS EQUAL COCK0002-DATA-MIN
               MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO   TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
               MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO  TO COCV5811-NIDINVOICE-S
               MOVE COCK0001-ERR-DDATAEMISS TO COCV5811-NIDINVOICE-MSG
               MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC       TO COCV5811-NIDINVOICE-CAPLIC
             END-IF
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF COCV5810-CMOEDA EQUAL SPACES
                MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV5811-CMOEDA-S
                MOVE COCK0001-MOEDA-OBRIGAT TO COCV5811-CMOEDA-MSG
                MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC        TO COCV5811-CMOEDA-CAPLIC
             END-IF
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF COCV5810-DDATAEMIS2 NOT EQUAL COCK0002-DATA-MIN
              IF COCV5810-CSTATUS NOT EQUAL COCK0002-CSTATUS-CANC
               IF COCV5810-REFINVOICE EQUAL SPACES
                 MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                 MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV5811-REFINVOICE-S
                 MOVE COCK0001-ZREF-OBRIGAT  TO COCV5811-REFINVOICE-MSG
                 MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC     TO COCV5811-REFINVOICE-CAPLIC
               END-IF
              END-IF
             END-IF
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF COCV5810-DDATEPAG NOT EQUAL COCK0002-DATA-MIN
               IF COCV5810-DDATEPAG < COCV5810-DDATAEMISS
                 MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                                           TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                 MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                                           TO COCV5811-DDATEPAG-S
                 MOVE COCK0001-DDATEPAG-MENOR
                                           TO COCV5811-DDATEPAG-MSG
                 MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC      TO COCV5811-DDATEPAG-CAPLIC
               END-IF
             END-IF
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF COCV5810-CTIPFAC EQUAL SPACES
               MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO    TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
               MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO   TO COCV5811-CTIPFAC-S
               MOVE COCK0001-CTIPFAC-OBRIGAT TO COCV5811-CTIPFAC-MSG
               MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC      TO COCV5811-CTIPFAC-CAPLIC
             END-IF
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2300-OBTEM-CEMPRESA
                 THRU 2399-OBTEM-CEMPRESA-EXIT
           END-IF.

      *---------------------------------------------------------------*
      *--- Valida se a Referencia da Factura em algum Projecto     ---*
      *--- com a mesma moeda. Se tiver a mesma moeda, é porque foi ---*
      *--- emitida pela mesma empresa.                             ---*
      *---------------------------------------------------------------*

           IF COCV5810-REFINVOICE NOT EQUAL SPACES

              MOVE COCV5810-NIDINVOICE   TO COCD5013-NIDINVOICE
              MOVE COCV5810-NIDPROJECTO  TO COCD5013-NIDPROJECTO
              MOVE COCV5810-REFINVOICE   TO COCD5013-GREFINV
              MOVE COCV5810-CMOEDA       TO COCD5013-CMOEDA
              MOVE COCD3605-CEMPRESA     TO COCD5013-CEMPRESA

              PERFORM 2110-OBTEM-NIDINVOICE
                 THRU 2110-OBTEM-NIDINVOICE-EXIT

           END-IF.

       2199-VALIDACOES-EXIT.
           EXIT.


      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                 2300-OBTEM-CEMPRESA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2300-OBTEM-CEMPRESA.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2300-OBTEM-CEMPRESA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCV5810-NIDPROJECTO  TO COCD3605-NIDPROJECTO.
           MOVE COCV5810-GCLIENTE     TO COCD3605-CLIENTE.

           EXEC SQL
                 SELECT  CEMPRESA, PAIS
                   INTO :COCD3605-CEMPRESA, :COCD3605-PAIS
                 FROM    COVT3605_PROJECTS
                 WHERE   NIDPROJECTO = :COCD3605-NIDPROJECTO
                   AND   CLIENTE     = :COCD3605-CLIENTE
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE CON-COVT3605 TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.
           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF NOT DB2-OK
                 MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                   TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                 MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                   TO COCV5811-NIDPROJECTO-S
                 MOVE COCK0001-NIDPROJECTO-N-EXISTS
                   TO COCV5811-NIDPROJECTO-MSG
                 MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC
                   TO COCV5811-NIDPROJECTO-CAPLIC
              END-IF
           END-IF.


       2399-OBTEM-CEMPRESA-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2110-OBT-STATUS-ANT
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2110-OBT-STATUS-ANT.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2110-OBT-STATUS-ANT  '     TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCV5810-NIDPROJECTO  TO COCD5013-NIDPROJECTO
           MOVE COCV5810-NIDINVOICE   TO COCD5013-NIDINVOICE

           EXEC SQL
                SELECT
                       CSTATUS
                     , CIMPOSTO
                     , NTOTALAMOUNT
                     , NTOTPAG
                     , NTAXPAG
                     , IRECON
                     , CPAIS
                     , CBANCO
                     , CCONTA
                     , DDATMOV
                     , NSEQMOV
                     , GREFNCR
                     , NTOTNCR
                 INTO  :COCD5013-CSTATUS
                     , :COCD5013-CIMPOSTO
                     , :COCD5013-NTOTALAMOUNT
                     , :COCD5013-NTOTPAG
                     , :COCD5013-NTAXPAG
                     , :COCD5013-IRECON
                     , :COCD5013-CPAIS
                     , :COCD5013-CBANCO
                     , :COCD5013-CCONTA
                     , :COCD5013-DDATMOV
                     , :COCD5013-NSEQMOV
                     , :COCD5013-GREFNCR
                     , :COCD5013-NTOTNCR
                  FROM  COVT5013_INVOICES
                 WHERE  NIDPROJECTO = :COCD5013-NIDPROJECTO
                   AND  NIDINVOICE  = :COCD5013-NIDINVOICE
           END-EXEC

           MOVE CON-COVT5013  TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2110-OBT-STATUS-ANT-EXIT'  TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              MOVE 'VIAL0002-IND-ERR'   TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(1)
              MOVE  VIAL0002-IND-ERROS  TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

       2110-OBT-STATUS-ANT-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2110-OBTEM-NIDINVOICE
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2110-OBTEM-NIDINVOICE.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2110-OBTEM-NIDINVOICE'     TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              MOVE 'COCD5013-GREFINV' TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(1)
              MOVE  COCD5013-GREFINV  TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

              EXEC SQL
                   SELECT
                          COUNT(NIDINVOICE)
                    INTO
                          :COCD5013-NIDINVOICE
                     FROM  COVT5013_INVOICES
                    WHERE  GREFINV     = :COCD5013-GREFINV
                      AND  CMOEDA      = :COCD5013-CMOEDA
                      AND  CEMPRESA    = :COCD5013-CEMPRESA
                      AND  (NIDPROJECTO <> :COCD5013-NIDPROJECTO
                      AND  NIDINVOICE  <> :COCD5013-NIDINVOICE)
              END-EXEC

              MOVE CON-COVT5013  TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME

              PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
                 THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT

              IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
                 IF COCD5013-NIDINVOICE > 0
                    MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                      TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                    MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                      TO COCV5811-REFINVOICE-S
                    MOVE COCK0001-MAIS-QUE-UM
                      TO COCV5811-REFINVOICE-MSG
                    MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC
                      TO COCV5811-REFINVOICE-CAPLIC
                 END-IF
              END-IF.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2110-OBTEM-NIDINVOICE-EXIT' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              MOVE 'SQLCODE         '   TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(1)
              MOVE  SQLCODE             TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
              MOVE 'VIAL0002-IND-ERR'   TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(2)
              MOVE  VIAL0002-IND-ERROS  TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(2)
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.


       2110-OBTEM-NIDINVOICE-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2100-VALIDA-IMPOSTO
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2100-VALIDA-IMPOSTO.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2100-VALIDA-IMPOSTO' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCK0002-EVEN-RECEITA    TO COCL5005-CTIP-EVEN
           MOVE COCV5810-NTOTALAMOUNT    TO COCL5005-NTOTALAMOUNT
           MOVE COCV5810-CIMPOSTO        TO COCL5005-CIMPOSTO
           MOVE COCV5810-CMOEDA          TO COCL5005-CMOEDA
           MOVE COCD3605-PAIS            TO COCL5005-CPAIS
           MOVE COCD3605-CEMPRESA        TO COCL5005-CEMPRESA
           MOVE ZEROS                    TO COCL5005-NTAXAMOUNT
           MOVE ZEROS                    TO COCL5005-NRETAMOUNT
           MOVE ZEROS                    TO COCL5005-NRETTAX
           MOVE COCD3605-NIDPROJECTO     TO COCL5005-NIDPROJECTO.
           MOVE ZEROES                   TO COCL5005-NIDINVOICE.
           MOVE SPACES                   TO COCL5005-GFORNECED.

           MOVE VIAL0001-DATA-PROCESSO-I TO COCL5005-DDATAEMISS.

           IF  COCV5810-DDATAEMISS NOT = SPACES AND
               COCV5810-DDATAEMISS NOT = COCK0002-DATA-MIN
               MOVE COCV5810-DDATAEMISS  TO COCL5005-DDATAEMISS
           END-IF.

           IF  COCV5810-DDATAEMIS2 NOT = SPACES AND
               COCV5810-DDATAEMIS2 NOT = COCK0002-DATA-MIN
               MOVE COCV5810-DDATAEMIS2  TO COCL5005-DDATAEMISS
           END-IF.

           INITIALIZE ETCL0002-COMMAREA  REPLACING NUMERIC BY ZEROES
                                              ALPHANUMERIC BY SPACES

           INITIALIZE ETCL0002-AREA-ERRO REPLACING NUMERIC BY ZEROES
                                              ALPHANUMERIC BY SPACES

           PERFORM ETCP0002-FORM-ONLINE-IN
              THRU ETCP0002-FORM-ONLINE-IN-EXIT

           PERFORM COCP5005-CALL-ROTINA
              THRU COCP5005-CALL-ROTINA-EXIT

           PERFORM ETCP0002-STD-END
              THRU ETCP0002-STD-END-EXIT

           IF NOT ETCL0002-SEM-ERROS
             MOVE ETCL0002-IND-ERROS     TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
             MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV5811-CIMPOSTO-S
             MOVE ETCL0002-NR-ERRO       TO COCV5811-CIMPOSTO-MSG
             MOVE ETCL0002-CAPLIC-ERRO   TO COCV5811-CIMPOSTO-CAPLIC
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2100-VALIDA-IMPOSTO-EXIT' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              MOVE 'COCL5005-NTAXAMOUNT' TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(1)
              MOVE  COCL5005-NTAXAMOUNT  TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
              MOVE 'COCL5005-NRETAMOUNT' TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(2)
              MOVE  COCL5005-NRETAMOUNT  TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(2)
              MOVE 'COCL5005-NRETTAX   ' TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(3)
              MOVE  COCL5005-NRETTAX     TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(3)
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

       2100-VALIDA-IMPOSTO-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2200-MODIFICA-DADOS
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2200-MODIFICA-DADOS.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2200-MODIFICA-DADOS' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *------------------------------------------------------------------
      *--- Se năo existirem pagamentos
      *---    COCD5013-NTOTPAG = zeros e COCD5013-NTAXPAG = zeros
      *--- executa um ciclo para ler todos os pagamentos existentes
      *--- na tabela COT64_INVPAY
      *--- para este NIDINVOICE/NIDPROJECTO e por cada um cria novo
      *--- registo igual com Valor Contrário (Estorno) nos campos
      *--- NTOTPAG, NTAXPAG, NTOTRET E NTAXRET
      *------------------------------------------------------------------
           IF  COCD5013-NTOTPAG = ZEROS
           AND COCD5013-NTAXPAG = ZEROS
               MOVE COCV5810-NIDINVOICE    TO WS-NIDINVOICE
               MOVE COCV5810-NIDPROJECTO   TO WS-NIDPROJECTO
               PERFORM 2300-ESTORNA-PAG
                  THRU 2300-ESTORNA-PAG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCV5810-NIDINVOICE    TO COCD5013-NIDINVOICE  .
           MOVE COCV5810-NIDPROJECTO   TO COCD5013-NIDPROJECTO .
           MOVE COCV5810-GCLIENTE      TO COCD5013-GCLIENTE    .
           MOVE COCV5810-DDATAINSER    TO COCD5013-DDATAINSER  .
           MOVE COCV5810-DDATAEMISS    TO COCD5013-DDATAEMISS  .
           MOVE COCV5810-DDATAEMIS2    TO COCD5013-DDATAEMIS2  .
           MOVE COCV5810-DDATEDUE      TO COCD5013-DDATEDUE    .
           MOVE COCV5810-CPRAZO        TO COCD5013-CPRAZO      .
           MOVE COCV5810-NTOTALAMOUNT  TO COCD5013-NTOTALAMOUNT.

           MOVE COCL5005-NTAXAMOUNT    TO COCD5013-NTAXAMOUNT
           MOVE COCL5005-NTAXAMOUNT    TO COCV5811-NTAXAMOUNT

           MOVE COCL5005-NRETAMOUNT    TO COCD5013-NTOTRET
           MOVE COCL5005-NRETTAX       TO COCD5013-NTAXRET

           MOVE COCV5810-GDESCINVOICE  TO COCD5013-GDESCINVOICE.

           IF COCV5810-CSTATUS EQUAL SPACES
              MOVE COCK0002-CSTATUS-PEMISS TO COCV5810-CSTATUS
           END-IF

           MOVE COCV5810-CSTATUS       TO COCD5013-CSTATUS     .
           MOVE VIAL0001-CUTILIZA-I    TO COCD5013-CUSERID     .
           MOVE COCV5810-REFINVOICE    TO COCD5013-GREFINV     .
           MOVE COCV5810-DDATEPAG      TO COCD5013-DPAG        .
           MOVE COCV5810-CMOEDA        TO COCD5013-CMOEDA      .
           MOVE COCV5810-CIMPOSTO      TO COCD5013-CIMPOSTO    .
           MOVE COCV5810-NOTAS         TO COCD5013-NOTAS       .
           MOVE COCV5810-CTIPFAC       TO COCD5013-CTIPFAC     .

           COMPUTE COCV5811-NVALTOT  = COCV5810-NTOTALAMOUNT +
                                       COCD5013-NTAXAMOUNT.

           COMPUTE COCV5811-NVALLIQ  = COCV5811-NVALTOT      -
                                      (COCV5811-NVALREC      +
                                       COCV5811-NTAXREC)     -
                                      (COCD5013-NTOTRET      +
                                       COCD5013-NTAXRET).

           IF COCV5810-NTOTALAMOUNT < 0
              MOVE COCK0002-NOTA-CREDITO TO COCD5013-CTIPDOC
           ELSE
              MOVE COCK0002-FACTURA      TO COCD5013-CTIPDOC
           END-IF.

           IF SW-DESFAZ-RECONC
              MOVE COCK0002-DATA-MIN     TO COCD5013-DDATMOV
              MOVE ZEROS                 TO COCD5013-NSEQMOV
              MOVE CON-N                 TO COCD5013-IRECON
              MOVE SPACES                TO COCD5013-CPAIS
                                            COCD5013-CBANCO
                                            COCD5013-CCONTA
           END-IF.

      *--- Memoriza dados para actualizar a Referencia nos Pagamentos
           MOVE COCV5810-REFINVOICE    TO WS-GREFINV           .
           MOVE COCV5810-NIDINVOICE    TO WS-CHAVE-NIDINVOICE  .
           MOVE COCV5810-NIDPROJECTO   TO WS-CHAVE-NIDPROJECTO .

           EXEC SQL
                UPDATE COVT5013_INVOICES
                SET
      *                NIDINVOICE   = :COCD5013-NIDINVOICE
      *              , NIDPROJECTO  = :COCD5013-NIDPROJECTO
                       GCLIENTE     = :COCD5013-GCLIENTE
                     , DDATAINSER   = :COCD5013-DDATAINSER
                     , DDATAEMISS   = :COCD5013-DDATAEMISS
                     , DDATAEMIS2   = :COCD5013-DDATAEMIS2
                     , DDATEDUE     = :COCD5013-DDATEDUE
                     , CPRAZO       = :COCD5013-CPRAZO
                     , NTOTALAMOUNT = :COCD5013-NTOTALAMOUNT
                     , NTAXAMOUNT   = :COCD5013-NTAXAMOUNT
                     , GDESCINVOICE = :COCD5013-GDESCINVOICE
                     , CSTATUS      = :COCD5013-CSTATUS
                     , CUSERID      = :COCD5013-CUSERID
                     , HTIMEST      =  CURRENT TIMESTAMP
                     , GREFINV      = :COCD5013-GREFINV
                     , DPAG         = :COCD5013-DPAG
                     , CTIPDOC      = :COCD5013-CTIPDOC
                     , CMOEDA       = :COCD5013-CMOEDA
                     , CIMPOSTO     = :COCD5013-CIMPOSTO
                     , NOTAS        = :COCD5013-NOTAS
                     , CTIPFAC      = :COCD5013-CTIPFAC
                     , NTOTPAG      = :COCD5013-NTOTPAG
                     , NTAXPAG      = :COCD5013-NTAXPAG
                     , NTOTRET      = :COCD5013-NTOTRET
                     , NTAXRET      = :COCD5013-NTAXRET
                     , IRECON       = :COCD5013-IRECON
                     , CPAIS        = :COCD5013-CPAIS
                     , CBANCO       = :COCD5013-CBANCO
                     , CCONTA       = :COCD5013-CCONTA
                     , DDATMOV      = :COCD5013-DDATMOV
                     , NSEQMOV      = :COCD5013-NSEQMOV
                 WHERE NIDINVOICE   = :COCD5013-NIDINVOICE
                   AND NIDPROJECTO  = :COCD5013-NIDPROJECTO
           END-EXEC.


           MOVE CON-COVT5013               TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF DB2-NOTFND
                 MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                   TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                    MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                      TO COCV5811-NIDINVOICE-S
                    MOVE COCK0001-NIDINVOICE-N-EXISTS
                      TO COCV5811-NIDINVOICE-MSG
                    MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC
                      TO COCV5811-NIDINVOICE-CAPLIC
              ELSE
                 IF NOT DB2-OK
                    MOVE VIAK0002-ABEND-DB2
                      TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                    MOVE VIAK0001-ERRO-DB2
                      TO VIAL0002-COD-ERRO-GRAVE
                 END-IF
              END-IF
           ELSE
              MOVE VIAK0002-ABEND-DB2
                TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
              MOVE VIAK0001-ERRO-DB2
                TO VIAL0002-COD-ERRO-GRAVE
           END-IF.

       2299-MODIFICA-DADOS-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2300-ESTORNA-PAG
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2300-ESTORNA-PAG.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2300-ESTORNA-PAG   ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

      *--- Limpa tabela interna
           MOVE ZEROS TO WS-X.
           PERFORM UNTIL WS-X > 99
                   ADD 1 TO WS-X
                   INITIALIZE WS-REG-64(WS-X)
           END-PERFORM.

      *--- Ler todos os pagamentos do documento e guardar na tabela interna
           MOVE ZEROS TO WS-X.
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2020-OPEN
                 THRU 2029-OPEN-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2030-FETCH
                 THRU 2039-FETCH-EXIT

              IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
                 IF DB2-OK
                    PERFORM 2040-CONTINUA
                       THRU 2049-CONTINUA-EXIT
                 END-IF
              END-IF
              PERFORM 2070-CLOSE
                 THRU 2079-CLOSE-EXIT
           END-IF.

      *--- Ler a tabela interna, mudar sinal e escrever nos pagamentos
           MOVE ZEROS TO WS-X.
           PERFORM UNTIL WS-X > 99
                   ADD 1 TO WS-X
                   IF WS-REG-64-NIDINVOICE(WS-X) NOT = ZEROS
                      MOVE WS-REG-64(WS-X) TO DCLCOCD6405

                      IF COCD6405-NTOTPAG NOT = ZEROS
                         MULTIPLY COCD6405-NTOTPAG BY -1
                            GIVING COCD6405-NTOTPAG
                      END-IF

                      IF COCD6405-NTAXPAG NOT = ZEROS
                         MULTIPLY COCD6405-NTAXPAG BY -1
                            GIVING COCD6405-NTAXPAG
                      END-IF

                      IF COCD6405-NTOTRET NOT = ZEROS
                         MULTIPLY COCD6405-NTOTRET BY -1
                            GIVING COCD6405-NTOTRET
                      END-IF

                      IF COCD6405-NTAXRET NOT = ZEROS
                         MULTIPLY COCD6405-NTAXRET BY -1
                            GIVING COCD6405-NTAXRET
                      END-IF

                      PERFORM 2700-INSERT
                         THRU 2700-INSERT-EXIT

                   END-IF
           END-PERFORM.

           IF SW-DESFAZ-RECONC
              IF COCD5013-NSEQMOV GREATER ZEROS
                 PERFORM 2900-UPD-MOV-BANC
                    THRU 2900-UPD-MOV-BANC-EXIT
              END-IF

              IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
                 PERFORM 2910-UPD-INVPAY
                    THRU 2910-UPD-INVPAY-EXIT
              END-IF
           END-IF.

       2300-ESTORNA-PAG-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                     2020-OPEN
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2020-OPEN.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2020-OPEN' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           EXEC SQL
               OPEN CURCOT64
           END-EXEC

           MOVE CON-COVT6405               TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

       2029-OPEN-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                     2030-FETCH
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2030-FETCH.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2030-FETCH' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           EXEC SQL
              FETCH CURCOT64
               INTO
                   :COCD6405-NIDINVOICE
                 , :COCD6405-NSEQ
                 , :COCD6405-NIDPROJECTO
                 , :COCD6405-GCLIENTE
                 , :COCD6405-DDATAINSER
                 , :COCD6405-DDATAEMISS
                 , :COCD6405-DDATAEMIS2
                 , :COCD6405-DDATEDUE
                 , :COCD6405-CPRAZO
                 , :COCD6405-NTOTALAMOUNT
                 , :COCD6405-NTAXAMOUNT
                 , :COCD6405-GDESCINVOICE
                 , :COCD6405-CSTATUS
                 , :COCD6405-CUSERID
                 , :COCD6405-HTIMEST
                 , :COCD6405-GREFINV
                 , :COCD6405-DPAG
                 , :COCD6405-CTIPDOC
                 , :COCD6405-CMOEDA
                 , :COCD6405-CIMPOSTO
                 , :COCD6405-NOTAS
                 , :COCD6405-NTOTCTRV
                 , :COCD6405-NTAXCTRV
                 , :COCD6405-CTIPFAC
                 , :COCD6405-NTOTPAG
                 , :COCD6405-NTAXPAG
                 , :COCD6405-NTOTRET
                 , :COCD6405-NTAXRET
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE CON-COVT6405               TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

       2039-FETCH-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                       2040-CONTINUA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2040-CONTINUA.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2040-CONTINUA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE ZEROES TO WS-X.
           MOVE ZEROES TO WS-SEQ.
           PERFORM 2050-TRATA-OCCURS
              THRU 2059-TRATA-OCCURS-EXIT
             UNTIL NOT DB2-OK
                OR NOT VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS.

       2049-CONTINUA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            2050-TRATA-OCCURS
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2050-TRATA-OCCURS.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2050-TRATA-OCCURS' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           ADD 1 TO WS-X.
           MOVE COCD6405-NIDINVOICE    TO WS-REG-64-NIDINVOICE(WS-X).
           MOVE COCD6405-NSEQ          TO WS-REG-64-NSEQ(WS-X).

           IF COCD6405-NSEQ > WS-SEQ
              MOVE COCD6405-NSEQ TO WS-SEQ
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCD6405-NIDPROJECTO   TO WS-REG-64-NIDPROJECTO(WS-X).
           MOVE COCD6405-GCLIENTE      TO WS-REG-64-GCLIENTE(WS-X).
           MOVE COCD6405-DDATAINSER    TO WS-REG-64-DDATAINSER(WS-X).
           MOVE COCD6405-DDATAEMISS    TO WS-REG-64-DDATAEMISS(WS-X).
           MOVE COCD6405-DDATAEMIS2    TO WS-REG-64-DDATAEMIS2(WS-X).
           MOVE COCD6405-DDATEDUE      TO WS-REG-64-DDATEDUE(WS-X).
           MOVE COCD6405-CPRAZO        TO WS-REG-64-CPRAZO(WS-X).
           MOVE COCD6405-NTOTALAMOUNT  TO WS-REG-64-NTOTALAMOUNT(WS-X).
           MOVE COCD6405-NTAXAMOUNT    TO WS-REG-64-NTAXAMOUNT(WS-X).
           MOVE COCD6405-GDESCINVOICE  TO WS-REG-64-GDESCINVOICE(WS-X).
           MOVE COCD6405-CSTATUS       TO WS-REG-64-CSTATUS(WS-X).
           MOVE COCD6405-CUSERID       TO WS-REG-64-CUSERID(WS-X).
           MOVE COCD6405-HTIMEST       TO WS-REG-64-HTIMEST(WS-X).
           MOVE COCD6405-GREFINV       TO WS-REG-64-GREFINV(WS-X).
           MOVE COCD6405-DPAG          TO WS-REG-64-DPAG(WS-X).
           MOVE COCD6405-CTIPDOC       TO WS-REG-64-CTIPDOC(WS-X).
           MOVE COCD6405-CMOEDA        TO WS-REG-64-CMOEDA(WS-X).
           MOVE COCD6405-CIMPOSTO      TO WS-REG-64-CIMPOSTO(WS-X).
           MOVE COCD6405-NOTAS         TO WS-REG-64-NOTAS(WS-X).
           MOVE COCD6405-NTOTCTRV      TO WS-REG-64-NTOTCTRV(WS-X).
           MOVE COCD6405-NTAXCTRV      TO WS-REG-64-NTAXCTRV(WS-X).
           MOVE COCD6405-CTIPFAC       TO WS-REG-64-CTIPFAC(WS-X).
           MOVE COCD6405-NTOTPAG       TO WS-REG-64-NTOTPAG(WS-X).
           MOVE COCD6405-NTAXPAG       TO WS-REG-64-NTAXPAG(WS-X).
           MOVE COCD6405-NTOTRET       TO WS-REG-64-NTOTRET(WS-X).
           MOVE COCD6405-NTAXRET       TO WS-REG-64-NTAXRET(WS-X).

           PERFORM 2030-FETCH
              THRU 2039-FETCH-EXIT.

       2059-TRATA-OCCURS-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                     2070-CLOSE
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2070-CLOSE.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2070-CLOSE' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           EXEC SQL
               CLOSE CURCOT64
           END-EXEC.

       2079-CLOSE-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                     2700-INSERT
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2700-INSERT.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2700-INSERT' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE VIAL0001-CUTILIZA-I    TO COCD6405-CUSERID.
           COMPUTE WS-SEQ = WS-SEQ + 1.

           EXEC SQL
                INSERT INTO COVT6405_INVPAY
                (
                   NIDINVOICE
                 , NSEQ
                 , NIDPROJECTO
                 , GCLIENTE
                 , DDATAINSER
                 , DDATAEMISS
                 , DDATAEMIS2
                 , DDATEDUE
                 , CPRAZO
                 , NTOTALAMOUNT
                 , NTAXAMOUNT
                 , GDESCINVOICE
                 , CSTATUS
                 , CUSERID
                 , HTIMEST
                 , GREFINV
                 , DPAG
                 , CTIPDOC
                 , CMOEDA
                 , CIMPOSTO
                 , NOTAS
                 , CTIPFAC
                 , NTOTPAG
                 , NTAXPAG
                 , NTOTRET
                 , NTAXRET
                )
                VALUES (
                       :COCD6405-NIDINVOICE
                     , :WS-SEQ
                     , :COCD6405-NIDPROJECTO
                     , :COCD6405-GCLIENTE
                     , :COCD6405-DDATAINSER
                     , :COCD6405-DDATAEMISS
                     , :COCD6405-DDATAEMIS2
                     , :COCD6405-DDATEDUE
                     , :COCD6405-CPRAZO
                     , :COCD6405-NTOTALAMOUNT
                     , :COCD6405-NTAXAMOUNT
                     , :COCD6405-GDESCINVOICE
                     , :COCD6405-CSTATUS
                     , :COCD6405-CUSERID
                     ,  CURRENT TIMESTAMP
                     , :COCD6405-GREFINV
                     , :COCD6405-DPAG
                     , :COCD6405-CTIPDOC
                     , :COCD6405-CMOEDA
                     , :COCD6405-CIMPOSTO
                     , :COCD6405-NOTAS
                     , :COCD6405-CTIPFAC
                     , :COCD6405-NTOTPAG
                     , :COCD6405-NTAXPAG
                     , :COCD6405-NTOTRET
                     , :COCD6405-NTAXRET
                )
           END-EXEC

           MOVE CON-COVT6405               TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF NOT DB2-OK
               MOVE VIAK0002-ABEND-DB2 TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
               MOVE VIAK0001-ERRO-DB2  TO VIAL0002-COD-ERRO-GRAVE
             END-IF
           END-IF.

       2700-INSERT-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2800-REFERENCIA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2800-REFERENCIA.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2800-REFERENCIA    ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           EXEC SQL
                UPDATE COVT6405_INVPAY
                SET
                       GREFINV      = :WS-GREFINV
                 WHERE NIDINVOICE   = :WS-CHAVE-NIDINVOICE
                   AND NIDPROJECTO  = :WS-CHAVE-NIDPROJECTO
           END-EXEC.


           MOVE CON-COVT6405               TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF DB2-NOTFND
                 CONTINUE
              ELSE
                 IF NOT DB2-OK
                    MOVE VIAK0002-ABEND-DB2
                      TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                    MOVE VIAK0001-ERRO-DB2
                      TO VIAL0002-COD-ERRO-GRAVE
                 END-IF
              END-IF
           ELSE
              MOVE VIAK0002-ABEND-DB2
                TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
              MOVE VIAK0001-ERRO-DB2
                TO VIAL0002-COD-ERRO-GRAVE
           END-IF.

       2800-REFERENCIA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            2900-UPD-MOV-BANC
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2900-UPD-MOV-BANC.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2900-UPD-MOV-BANC'        TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCD5013-CPAIS           TO COCD6900-CPAIS.
           MOVE COCD5013-CBANCO          TO COCD6900-CBANCO.
           MOVE COCD5013-CCONTA          TO COCD6900-CCONTA.
           MOVE COCD5013-DDATMOV         TO COCD6900-DDATMOV.
           MOVE COCD5013-NSEQMOV         TO COCD6900-NSEQMOV.
           MOVE CON-N                    TO COCD6900-IRECON.
           MOVE SPACES                   TO COCD6900-GREFINV
           MOVE VIAL0001-CUTILIZA-I      TO COCD6900-CUSERID.

           EXEC SQL
                 UPDATE COVT6900_MOVBANC
                 SET    IRECON       = :COCD6900-IRECON
                      , GREFINV      = :COCD6900-GREFINV
                      , NINVREC      =  NINVREC - 1
                      , CUSERID      = :COCD6900-CUSERID
                      , HTIMEST      =  CURRENT TIMESTAMP
                  WHERE CPAIS        = :COCD6900-CPAIS
                    AND CBANCO       = :COCD6900-CBANCO
                    AND CCONTA       = :COCD6900-CCONTA
                    AND DDATMOV      = :COCD6900-DDATMOV
                    AND NSEQMOV      = :COCD6900-NSEQMOV
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE CON-COVT6900               TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF DB2-OK
                CONTINUE
             ELSE
               IF DB2-NOTFND
                 MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                 MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                                      TO COCV5811-NIDPROJECTO-S
                 MOVE COCK0001-SEM-MOV-RECONC
                                      TO COCV5811-NIDPROJECTO-MSG
                 MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC TO COCV5811-NIDPROJECTO-CAPLIC
               ELSE
                 MOVE VIAK0002-ABEND-DB2 TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                 MOVE VIAK0001-ERRO-DB2  TO VIAL0002-COD-ERRO-GRAVE
               END-IF
             END-IF
           END-IF.

       2900-UPD-MOV-BANC-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                 2910-UPD-INVPAY
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2910-UPD-INVPAY.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2910-UPD-INVPAY  ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCK0002-DATA-MIN        TO WS-DDATMOV
           MOVE ZEROS                    TO WS-NSEQMOV
           MOVE CON-N                    TO WS-IRECON
           MOVE SPACES                   TO WS-CPAIS
                                            WS-CBANCO
                                            WS-CCONTA

           MOVE COCV5810-NIDINVOICE      TO COCD6405-NIDINVOICE
           MOVE COCV5810-NIDPROJECTO     TO COCD6405-NIDPROJECTO
           MOVE VIAL0001-CUTILIZA-I      TO COCD6405-CUSERID

           EXEC SQL
                UPDATE COVT6405_INVPAY
                SET    IRECON       = :WS-IRECON
                  ,    CPAIS        = :WS-CPAIS
                  ,    CBANCO       = :WS-CBANCO
                  ,    CCONTA       = :WS-CCONTA
                  ,    DDATMOV      = :WS-DDATMOV
                  ,    NSEQMOV      = :WS-NSEQMOV
                  ,    CUSERID      = :COCD6405-CUSERID
                  ,    HTIMEST      =  CURRENT TIMESTAMP
                 WHERE NIDINVOICE   = :COCD6405-NIDINVOICE
                   AND NIDPROJECTO  = :COCD6405-NIDPROJECTO
                   AND IRECON      <> :CON-S
           END-EXEC.


           MOVE CON-COVT6405               TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF DB2-NOTFND
                 CONTINUE
              ELSE
                 IF NOT DB2-OK
                    MOVE VIAK0002-ABEND-DB2
                      TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                    MOVE VIAK0001-ERRO-DB2
                      TO VIAL0002-COD-ERRO-GRAVE
                 END-IF
              END-IF
           ELSE
              MOVE VIAK0002-ABEND-DB2
                TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
              MOVE VIAK0001-ERRO-DB2
                TO VIAL0002-COD-ERRO-GRAVE
           END-IF.

       2910-UPD-INVPAY-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2250-GERA-GATILHO.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2250-GERA-GATILHO.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2250-GERA-GATILHO   ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCK0002-GAT-INV-AMOUNT   TO COCL0030-CGATILHO.
           MOVE COCD5013-NIDPROJECTO      TO COCL0030-CCHAVE.
           MOVE SPACES                    TO COCL0030-GDESC.

           MOVE COCD5013-NIDINVOICE       TO WS-GAT-NIDINVOICE.
           MOVE COCD5013-NTOTALAMOUNT     TO WS-GAT-AMOUNT-ANT.
           MOVE COCV5810-NTOTALAMOUNT     TO WS-GAT-AMOUNT-POS.
           MOVE WS-GAT-AMOUNT             TO COCL0030-DADOS.

           PERFORM ETCP0002-FORM-ONLINE-IN
              THRU ETCP0002-FORM-ONLINE-IN-EXIT.

           PERFORM COCP0030-CALL-ROTINA
              THRU COCP0030-CALL-ROTINA-EXIT.

           PERFORM ETCP0002-STD-END
              THRU ETCP0002-STD-END-EXIT.

       2250-GERA-GATILHO-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              MOVE 'COCV5811-NTOTALAMOUNT-A' TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(1)
              MOVE  COCV5811-NTOTALAMOUNT-A  TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
              MOVE 'COCV5811-NVALTOT       ' TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(2)
              MOVE  COCV5811-NVALTOT         TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(2)
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCV5811-MSG               TO VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-OUTPUT.
           MOVE COCV5811-LENGTH            TO VIAL0001-LENGTH-MSG.
           MOVE COCV5811-NR-CAMPOS         TO VIAL0001-NR-CAMPOS.
           MOVE ZEROES
             TO VIAL0001-OCORRENCIAS.

       3099-FINAL-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *==============================================================
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE VIAP0003 END-EXEC.
      *==============================================================
           COPY VIAP0010.
           COPY VIAP0016.
           COPY COCP5005.
           COPY ETCP0002.
           COPY AQCP0005.
           COPY COCP0030.
